tora-san 's lullaby ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō ) is a 1974 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and reiko &lt;unk&gt; as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san 's lullaby was released on december 28 , 1974 , by republic pictures .